The Insurance Analytics Dashboard is a data visualization project built using Power BI to analyze insurance data and uncover business insights related to customers, policies, claims, and revenue performance.

This dashboard helps stakeholders understand insurance trends, customer behavior, claim patterns, and overall company performance through interactive visualizations.

Project Objectives
Analyze insurance policy distribution and performance
Track claim amount and approval trends
Understand customer demographics
Identify high-risk segments
Support data-driven decision making

Dataset Description

The dataset contains insurance-related information such as:

Customer Details
Policy Type
Premium Amount
Claim Amount
Claim Status
Policy Duration
Gender / Age Group
Region / Location

